      </nav>
      <h1>Idaho Commercial Vehicle Registration Guide</h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">IRP, IFTA, UCR & HVUT Requirements</p>
      <p class="hero-intro">Operating a commercial truck in Idaho means keeping multiple registrations and filings current. Miss one deadline, and you're parked - or worse, fined. This guide covers what Idaho-based carriers need to stay legal on the road.</p>
    </div>
